│   └── evidence.csv
├── docs/
│   └── methodology.md
├── results/
├── src/agegate_harms/
│   ├── cli.py
│   ├── model.py
│   └── reporting.py
└── tests/
    └── test_model.py
```

## What the experiment does not do

It does not decide whether an age restriction is justified, estimate health benefits, provide legal advice, validate a vendor, or treat identity checks as morally interchangeable. Those require separate evidence and normative analysis.
